# Images Folder

Put all your product and company images in this folder.

## Recommended Image Names
```
hero.jpg          ← Homepage background image (optional)
about.jpg         ← About section company photo
factory.jpg       ← Factory / workshop photo
pump-casing.jpg   ← Product: pump casing
impeller.jpg      ← Product: impeller
valve-body.jpg    ← Product: valve body
flange.jpg        ← Product: flange
gearbox.jpg       ← Product: gearbox housing
agri-parts.jpg    ← Product: agricultural parts
custom-parts.jpg  ← Product: custom parts
bearing-housing.jpg ← Product: bearing housing
team.jpg          ← Company team photo (optional)
```

## Image Requirements
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Recommended size: 800×600px (product images), 1920×1080px (hero/about images)
- Max file size: 500KB per image
- Naming: lowercase with hyphens (e.g., `pump-casing.jpg`)
